]] at the [[Miss Universe 2018]].<ref name=klip/><ref name=page/><ref name=sorry/><ref name=klip/><ref name=page/><ref name=sorry/> \n\n==Personal life==\nSejdini was born in [[Elbasan]], [[Albania]] in 2000. In addition to her native language (Albanian), she speaks 3 foreign languages, namely Italian, French and English.<ref name=lives/> <ref name=lives/> She lives in [[Tirana]].<ref name=lives/> Sejdini joined various clips<ref>[http://archive.is/pFhiq] {{dead link|date=July 2019}}</ref> as a model (the most famous are ''Gang gang'' by Fero<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fero - Gang Gang|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7IThtyR220|website=Youtube.com|access-date=2018-12-17}}</ref> and ''Jealousy'' by Mozzik)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdwViLd4yK8|title=YouTube|website=Youtube.com}}</ref> in [[Albania]]. Sejdini participated, at the age of 16,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.revistavip.club/njihuni-trejsi-sejdini-konkurrente-e-miss-universe-albania-2016/|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331011638/http://www.revistavip.club/njihuni-trejsi-sejdini-konkurrente-e-miss-universe-albania-2016/|url-status=dead|title=Njihuni me Trejsi Sejdini, konkurrente e Miss Universe Albania 2016|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.missosology.info/forum/viewtopic.php|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331010455/http://www.missosology.info/forum/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=963918|url-status=dead|title=Could Trejsi Sejdini win MISS UNIVERSE ?|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://albanianbeauty.wordpress.com/2016/05/16/miss-albania-universe-2016-contestants/|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331010220/https://albanianbeauty.wordpress.com/2016/05/16/miss-albania-universe-2016-contestants/|url-status=dead|title=MISS ALBANIA UNIVERSE 2016 Contestants|date=May 16, 2016|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> in ''[[Miss Universe Albania]] 2016'' pageant,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Public-Figure/trejsisejdinimiss/about/|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331005827/https://www.facebook.com/pg/trejsisejdinimiss/about/?ref=page_internal|url-status=dead|title=Trejsi Sejdini - Miss Universe Albania 2016|website=Facebook.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pageantsnews.com/en/news/international-contests/miss-universe/4092-miss-albania-universe-2016-meet-the-candidates|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331011604/https://pageantsnews.com/en/news/international-contests/miss-universe/4092-miss-albania-universe-2016-meet-the-candidates|url-status=dead|title=Miss Albania Universe 2016 : Meet the candidates|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> but she did not win even though she was one of the favorite competitors.<ref>[http://archive.today/585BK]</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thegreatpageantcommunity.com/2016/04/18/miss-universe-albania-2016-meet-contestants/|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331011537/https://thegreatpageantcommunity.com/2016/04/18/miss-universe-albania-2016-meet-contestants/|url-status=dead|title=Miss Universe Albania 2016 [Meet the Contestants]|date=April 17, 2016|website=Thegreatpageantcommunity.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> She won<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.oranews.tv/article/shpallet-miss-universe-albania-ja-kush-do-na-perfaqesoje-ne-amerike|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331013442/http://www.oranews.tv/article/shpallet-miss-universe-albania-ja-kush-do-na-perfaqesoje-ne-amerike|url-status=dead|title=Shpallet Miss Universe Albania, ja kush do na p\u00ebrfaq\u00ebsoj\u00eb n\u00eb Amerik\u00eb|website=Oranews.tv|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> the ''[[Miss Universe Albania]] 2018'' pageant in June 2018 at ''Pallati i Kongreseve''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://awardgoesto.com/miss-universe-albania-2018-trejsi-sejdini/|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331003724/http://awardgoesto.com/miss-universe-albania-2018-trejsi-sejdini/|url-status=dead|title=Miss Universe Albania 2018 award goes to Trejsi Sejdini|date=June 19, 2018|website=Awardgoesto.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rankmylist.com/list/who-will-win-miss-universe-2018/trejsi-sejdini-albania/9aa6034ece0|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331010714/https://www.rankmylist.com/list/who-will-win-miss-universe-2018/trejsi-sejdini-albania/9aa6034ece0|url-status=dead|title=Trejsi Sejdini (Albania) [Who will win Miss Universe 2018?]|website=Rankmylist.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> She represented, at the age of 18,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/MemesQueenOficial/posts/1739855596098500|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331013428/https://www.facebook.com/MemesQueenOficial/posts/trejsi-sejdini-miss-albania-universo-2018-tiene-18-a%C3%B1os-y-183m-de-estatura-insol/1739855596098500/%23|url-status=dead|title=MEMES QUEEN|website=Facebook.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/culture/net/2018/12/14/why-thai-fans-are-all-about-miss-universe-albania/|title=Why Thai Fans Are All About Miss Universe Albania|first1=Asaree|last1=Thaitrakulpanich|first2=Staff|last2=Reporter|date=December 14, 2018}}</ref> her country ([[Albania]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.globalbeauties.com/news/2018/6/7/miss-universe-albania-2018-crowned|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331012539/https://www.globalbeauties.com/news/2018/6/7/miss-universe-albania-2018-crowned|url-status=dead|title=Miss Universe Albania 2018 Crowned|website=Globalbeauties.com|archive-date=23 July 2019}}</ref> at the ''[[Miss Universe 2018]]'' pageant in December 2018.<ref name=lives/> \n\n==Pageantry==\n===Miss Universe Albania 2018===\nSejdini was crowned<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newsbomb.al/trejsi-sejdini-shpallet-fituese-e-miss-universe-albania-fotot-123521|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20190331014048/https://www.newsbomb.al/trejsi-sejdini-shpallet-fituese-e-miss-universe-albania-fotot-123521|url-status=dead|title=Trejsi Sejdini shpallet fituese e 