ss Universe Albania|Miss Universe Albania 2016]] \n| competitions = Miss Europe Continental 2015<br>(Winner)<br>[[Miss Universe Albania|Miss Universe Albania 2016]]<br>(Winner)<br>[[Miss Universe 2016]]<br>(Miss Photogenic)<ref name=\"Special awards\">{{Cite news |url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/life/01/30/17/who-won-miss-congeniality-miss-photogenic-in-miss-universe-pageant |title=Who won Miss Congeniality, Miss Photogenic in Miss Universe pageant? |last=Domingo |first=Katrina |date=January 30, 2017 |publisher=[[ABS-CBN News]] |access-date=January 30, 2017}}</ref>\n| height ={{height|m=1.78|precision=0}}\n| measurements =\n}}\n\n'''Lindita Idrizi''' (born April 11, 1996) is an Albanian model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned [[Miss Universe Albania|Miss Universe Albania 2016]] and represented [[Albania]] at the [[Miss Universe 2016]].\n\n==Early life==\nIdrizi works as a model in [[Albania]].\n\n==Pageantry==\n===Miss Universe Albania 2016===\nIdrizi was crowned Miss Universe Albania 2016 at the end of the pageant on June 2, 2016. This year a total of 28 contestants competed for the title.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pageantsnews.com/lindita-idrizi-miss-universe-albania-2016/|title=Lindita Idrizi is Miss Universe Albania 2016|date=2 June 2016|website=Pageants News}}</ref>\n\n===Miss Universe 2016===\nIdrizi represented [[Albania]] at the [[Miss Universe 2016]]. Idrizi was awarded Miss Photogenic.<ref name=\"Special awards\"/>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://revistavip.club/ Official website]\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-ach}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Megi Luka]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Miss Universe Albania]]\n|years=2016}}\n{{S-aft|after=[[Blerta Leka]]}}\n{{S-bef|before={{Flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Samantha McClung]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Miss Photogenic]]\n|years=2016}}\n{{S-aft|after={{Flagicon|India}} [[Nehal Chudasama]]\n|years=2018}}\n{{S-end}}\n{{Miss Universe 2016 delegates}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Idrizi, Lindita}}\n[[Catego